PN,30901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782776882
OL,3,CAsylum seekers to pay up to #10k
OL,4,Ctowards cost of accommodation and
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThe Home Secretary has announced a new
OL,8,Fpolicy where asylum seekers will be
OL,9,Fmade to pay up to #10,000 towards the
OL,10,Fcost of their accommodation and
OL,11,Fsupport, once they start earning.
OL,13,FThe new plan requires them to pay off
OL,14,Fthe full amount before they can be
OL,15,Fconsidered for settled status.
OL,17,FEligible adults will likely pay off an
OL,18,Famount each month above a set
OL,19,Fthreshold ` similar to a student loan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782776882
OL,3,CAsylum seekers to pay up to #10k
OL,4,Ctowards cost of accommodation and
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FMigrants need settled status, or
OL,8,FIndefinite Leave to Remain, to be able
OL,9,Fto permanently live, work, and study
OL,10,Fin the UK.
OL,12,FThe government said it spent #4
OL,13,Fbillion on accommodation and support
OL,14,Ffor asylum seekers in 2025 and the
OL,15,FHome Office estimates the average cost
OL,16,Fper person per night of accommodating
OL,17,Fasylum seekers is #23.25 in dispersal
OL,18,Faccommodation (longer term temporary
OL,19,Fhousing) and #144 in hotels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782776882
OL,3,CAsylum seekers to pay up to #10k
OL,4,Ctowards cost of accommodation and
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FSubsistence payments range between
OL,8,F#9.95 to #49.18 per person per week.
OL,10,FShabana Mahmood has said the cost is
OL,11,F"too high" but points to the reduction
OL,12,Fof "asylum costs by #1 billion" so far.
OL,14,FShe said it is right that we ask those
OL,15,Fwho can contribute to do so, saying
OL,16,F"receiving asylum support is a right,
OL,17,Fbut it is also a responsibility" and
OL,18,Fsaid that when people can "contribute
OL,19,Fand repay the generosity of the
OL,20,FBritish people, we expect them to do
OL,21,Fso".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782776882
OL,3,CAsylum seekers to pay up to #10k
OL,4,Ctowards cost of accommodation and
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThe Home Office said that those liable
OL,8,Ffor the cost who leave the UK will be
OL,9,Fmade to pay in full if they want to
OL,10,Fcome back at a future date
OL,12,FThe powers needed to recover the costs
OL,13,Fwill be set out by the Immigration and
OL,14,FAsylum Bill when it is introduce to
OL,15,FParliament on Tuesday.
OL,17,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782776882
OL,3,CAsylum seekers to pay up to #10k
OL,4,Ctowards cost of accommodation and
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FDr Madeleine Sumption, director of the
OL,8,FMigration Observatory at the
OL,9,FUniversity of Oxford, said it was
OL,10,Flikely that only a relatively small
OL,11,Fshare of people granted asylum would
OL,12,Factually earn enough to pay towards
OL,13,Fthe scheme, and warned it could
OL,14,Fdiscourage asylum seekers from working
OL,15,Fto avoid the cost.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782776882
OL,3,CAsylum seekers to pay up to #10k
OL,4,Ctowards cost of accommodation and
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"The data suggests that unless
OL,8,Fthresholds were significantly below
OL,9,Fthe minimum wage, a relatively small
OL,10,Fshare of people granted asylum would
OL,11,Fearn enough to make contributions to
OL,12,Fthe scheme," she said.
OL,14,F"The impact of the scheme on public
OL,15,Ffinances is likely to be relatively
OL,16,Fsmall, because it is a means-tested
OL,17,Fpayment for a very low-income
OL,18,Fpopulation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@LO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782776882
OL,3,CAsylum seekers to pay up to #10k
OL,4,Ctowards cost of accommodation and
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"It is possible that the scheme could
OL,8,Fhave some other impacts, such as
OL,9,Fdiscouraging asylum seekers from
OL,10,Ftaking up accommodation if they can
OL,11,Ffind other support (such as family
OL,12,Fmembers or a charity), or discouraging
OL,13,Fthem from working once they get
OL,14,Frefugee status because they face a
OL,15,Fhigher effective tax rate."
OL,17,FShe said that it would be hard to
OL,18,Fpredict the impact of the reforms and
OL,19,Fthat the #10,000 cost may not line up
OL,20,Fwith the actual cost.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782776882
OL,3,CAsylum seekers to pay up to #10k
OL,4,Ctowards cost of accommodation and
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FShe gave an example: "The cost of
OL,8,Fsupporting person who waits for a year
OL,9,Fin a hotel would be over #50,000,
OL,10,Fwhile the cost for someone in much
OL,11,Fcheaper HMO (house in multiple
OL,12,Foccupation) accommodation who only
OL,13,Fwaits six months would be under
OL,14,F#6,000."
OL,16,FZoe Dexter, from the Helen Bamber
OL,17,FFoundation human rights charity,
OL,18,Fcriticised the plan and said it was
OL,19,F"more performative cruelty from the
OL,20,Fgovernment" and "is the opposite of
OL,21,Fintegration".
OL,26,@vD@HO]{D@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782776882
OL,3,CAsylum seekers to pay up to #10k
OL,4,Ctowards cost of accommodation and
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"These are people who have fled
OL,8,Fpersecution and extreme violence,
OL,9,Foften arriving with nothing, before
OL,10,Fspending months or years in
OL,11,Fovercrowded, dilapidated
OL,12,Faccommodation, sometimes facing
OL,13,Fintimidation and violent protests
OL,14,Foutside the places they are housed,"
OL,15,Fshe said.
OL,17,F"Burdening them with debt just as they
OL,18,Fbegin rebuilding their lives is
OL,19,Fgrossly unjust and entirely self-
OL,20,Fdefeating."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782776882
OL,3,CAsylum seekers to pay up to #10k
OL,4,Ctowards cost of accommodation and
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FShadow home secretary Chris Philp
OL,8,Fclaimed it was a policy put forward by
OL,9,Fthe Conservatives, calling it
OL,10,F"flattering".
OL,12,F"This precise scheme was proposed by
OL,13,Fus in an amendment to the Immigration
OL,14,FBill last year, which Labour blocked,"
OL,15,Fhe said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782776882
OL,3,CAsylum seekers to pay up to #10k
OL,4,Ctowards cost of accommodation and
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FIt comes after the Home Office
OL,8,Frevealed it is planning to use more
OL,9,Fformer military barracks to house
OL,10,Fthousands of asylum seekers in its
OL,11,Fquest to shut all asylum hotels by the
OL,12,Fnext election.
OL,14,FThe number of people being housed in
OL,15,Fhotels has fallen to its lowest level
OL,16,Fsince data was first reported in 2022,
OL,17,Faccording to Home Office figures
OL,18,Fpublished last month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782776882
OL,3,CAsylum seekers to pay up to #10k
OL,4,Ctowards cost of accommodation and
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FOther reforms set to be laid out on
OL,8,FTuesday include creating a "single
OL,9,Froute" that prevents migrants from
OL,10,Fappealing against a rejected claim and
OL,11,Ffrom bringing further claims about new
OL,12,Fmatters before their removal.
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
